*Aquaculture at Euro Tier
*16 -- 19 November 2010 -- HANOVER
Aquaculture continues to grow significantly at EuroTier. This sector 
combines innovative energy and nutrient concepts. We have continually 
expanded this segment and more companies now realize the potential of 
what we have to offer. Because EuroTier encompasses important animal 
species such as pig and cattle, there are many synergies, for example in 
the area of bioenergy which is extensively covered here. However, we 
also see more and more pig and cattle farms with bioenergy extending 
their current operations to include aquaculture. As all sectors are 
represented here at EuroTier, many feel it is worthwhile coming here to 
explore potential business activities in other sectors," says Dr. Birgit 
Schmidt-Puckhaber, project manager for aquaculture within the DLG.

