<http://www.eurotier.de/news.html?wb328=aHR0cDovL3ByZXNzZS5kbGcub3JnOjgwODEvL3B1YmxpY0FydGlrZWxEZXRhaWwuZG8%2Fc3ViPWV1cm90aWVyJmFydGlrZWxJZD0zNjQ5JmthdGVnb3JpZUlkPTEzJnNwcmFjaGVJZD0yJmJlcmVpY2g9TmV3cw%3D%3D> 
about aquaculture at EuroTier, including the independent advice centre 
with experts from leading aquaculture Institutes such as IMARES of 
