                      This conference is co-organized with the 8th ECPA,
                      the 8th EFITA conferences as there is an
                      established tradition of bringing ECPA and ECPLF
                      together.<br>
                      The deadline for submitting the full paper is till
                      30th November 2010 with no exception.<br>
                      This conference has no limit for length of full
                      paper. In case, recommended length for full paper
                      is above 8 pages.<br>
                      See: <a href="http://www.ecplf2011.cz/">http://www.ecplf2011.cz</a>
                      <br>
                      Contact: Eva CERVENKOVA<br>
                      E-mail: conference2011(a)czu.cz <br>
