                    <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3"><br>
                      <b>The ring of a telephone - that'll do it!<br>
                      </b>A dog lover, whose dog was a bitch, and 'in
                      heat', agreed to look after and house her
                      neighbour's male dog, while they were away on
                      vacation.<br>
                      <br>
                      She had a large house and believed that she could
                      keep them apart, but as she was drifting off to
                      sleep she heard awful howling and moaning sounds,
                      rushed downstairs and found the dogs locked
                      together, in obvious pain and unable to disengage,
                      as so frequently happens when they mate.<br>
                      <br>
                      Unable to separate them and perplexed as to what
                      to do next, although it was late, she called the
                      vet, who answered in a very grumpy voice.<br>
                      <br>
                      Having explained the problem to him, the vet said.
                      "Hang up the phone and place it down alongside the
                      dogs. I will then call you back and the noise of
                      the ringing will make the male lose his erection
                      and he will be able to withdraw".<br>
                      <br>
                      "Do you think that will work?" she asked.<br>
                      <br>
                      "It just worked for me!" he replied.<br>
                      <br>
                    </font><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>
                      <b>D&eacute;claration C.N.I.L. num&eacute;ro 667690</b><br>
                      Vous &ecirc;tes plus de 28 000 &agrave; recevoir "Du c&ocirc;t&eacute; du
                      web et de l'informatique agricole". La
                      reproduction n'est autoris&eacute;e que pour votre usage
                      personnel et les besoins de votre entreprise.<br>
                      Si vous souhaitez abonner un (e) ami (e), un (e)
                      coll&egrave;gue ou encore vous d&eacute;sabonner (loi No 78-17
                      du 6 janvier 1978), et bien s&ucirc;r contribuer &agrave; la
                      r&eacute;daction de cette gazette presque hebdomadaire,
                      merci d'en faire directement la demande &agrave; Guy
                      Waksman.<br>
                      ACTA Informatique est partenaire France T&eacute;l&eacute;com
                      (SDSL et OLEANE), distributeur des routeurs CISCO
                      et des firewall WATCHGUARD et CISCO.<br>
                      ACTA Informatique r&eacute;alise des sites Internet aussi
                      bien que des applications pour PC sous WINDOWS, et
                      propose un grand nombre de stages de formation.</font></td>
